## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the evolution of management roles. Additionally, the information is limited to the sources accessed, which may not reflect the most recent developments in management practices. Further research, including interviews with current managers and industry experts, could provide a more comprehensive view of the changes in management roles.